import React, { useEffect, useRef } from "react"; import '../../component/grid.css'; import '../home/home.css'; import '../../component/style.css'; import '../home/responsive.css'; import banner1 from '../img/banner_img1.jpg'; import banner2 from '../img/banner_img2.jpg'; import banner3 from '../img/banner_img3.jpg'; import banner4 from '../img/banner_img4.jpg'; import banner5 from '../img/banner_img5.jpg'; const Home = () => { const listImgRef = useRef(null); const imgsRef = useRef([]); const btnLeftRef = useRef(null); const btnRightRef = useRef(null); const dotsRef = useRef([]); useEffect(() => { const listImg = listImgRef.current; const imgs = imgsRef.current; const btnLeft = btnLeftRef.current; const btnRight = btnRightRef.current; const dots = dotsRef.current; let current = 0; const updateSlider = () => { let width = imgs[0]?.offsetWidth || 0; listImg.style.transform = `translateX(${-width * current}px)`; document.querySelector('.active')?.classList.remove('active'); dots[current]?.classList.add('active'); }; const toRight = () => { current = (current === imgs.length - 1) ? 0 : current + 1; updateSlider(); }; const toLeft = () => { current = (current === 0) ? imgs.length - 1 : current - 1; updateSlider(); }; let autoChange = setInterval(toRight, 4000); const handleRightClick = () => { clearInterval(autoChange); toRight(); autoChange = setInterval(toRight, 4000); }; const handleLeftClick = () => { clearInterval(autoChange); toLeft(); autoChange = setInterval(toRight, 4000); }; btnRight?.addEventListener('click', handleRightClick); btnLeft?.addEventListener('click', handleLeftClick); dots.forEach((dot, index) => { dot.addEventListener('click', () => { current = index; updateSlider(); clearInterval(autoChange); autoChange = setInterval(toRight, 4000); }); }); return () => { clearInterval(autoChange); btnRight?.removeEventListener('click', handleRightClick); btnLeft?.removeEventListener('click', handleLeftClick); dots.forEach((dot) => dot.removeEventListener('click', () => { })); }; }, []); return ( <>
